dc_title_s: South America, Peru, South Pacific Ocean, Caleta Lobitos, including Cabo Blanco (Raster Image)
dc_description_s: Prepared and published by Defense Mapping Agency Hydrographic/Topographic Center. Depths shown by isolines and soundings. Relief shown by contours, hachures, and spot heights. "From Peruvian charts to 1988." "Copyright restrictions of the country of origin continue to exist." "Soundings in meters." Inset: Cabo Blanco anchorage. Scale 1:15,000. Includes source listing and tidal information. Map No. 22126. This map is part of a collection of scanned and georeferenced nautical charts produced by the National Geospatial-Intelligence Agency (NGA).
